{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.1","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:1","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.001.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Sur l\u2019av\u00e8nement du Seigneur<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. (1 Ti 4:1. 1 Jn 2:18; 4:1-3.) Ap 13; 17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Pour ce qui concerne l\u2019av\u00e8nement de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ et notre r\u00e9union avec lui, nous vous prions, fr\u00e8res,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.1.12","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 1:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.1.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.2","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:2","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>de ne pas vous laisser facilement \u00e9branler dans votre bon sens, et de ne pas vous laisser troubler, soit par quelque inspiration, soit par quelque parole, ou par quelque lettre qu\u2019on dirait venir de nous, comme si le jour du Seigneur \u00e9tait d\u00e9j\u00e0 l\u00e0.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.3","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:3","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Que personne ne vous s\u00e9duise d\u2019aucune mani\u00e8re; car il faut que l\u2019apostasie soit arriv\u00e9e auparavant, et qu\u2019on ait vu para\u00eetre l\u2019homme du p\u00e9ch\u00e9, le fils de la perdition,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.4","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.4","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:4","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>l\u2019adversaire qui s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve au-dessus de tout ce qu\u2019on appelle Dieu ou de ce qu\u2019on adore, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 s\u2019asseoir dans le temple de Dieu, se proclamant lui-m\u00eame Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.5","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.5","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:5","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ne vous souvenez-vous pas que je vous disais ces choses, lorsque j\u2019\u00e9tais encore chez vous?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.6","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.4","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.6","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:6","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et maintenant vous savez ce qui le retient, afin qu\u2019il ne paraisse qu\u2019en son temps.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.7","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.5","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.7","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:7","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Car le myst\u00e8re de l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 agit d\u00e9j\u00e0; il faut seulement que celui qui le retient encore ait disparu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.8","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.6","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.8","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:8","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et alors para\u00eetra l\u2019impie, que le Seigneur J\u00e9sus d\u00e9truira par le souffle de sa bouche, et qu\u2019il an\u00e9antira par l\u2019\u00e9clat de son av\u00e8nement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.9","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.7","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.9","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:9","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>L\u2019apparition de cet impie se fera, par la puissance de Satan, avec toutes sortes de miracles, de signes et de prodiges mensongers,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.10","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.8","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.10","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:10","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>et avec toutes les s\u00e9ductions de l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 pour ceux qui p\u00e9rissent parce qu\u2019ils n\u2019ont pas re\u00e7u l\u2019amour de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 pour \u00eatre sauv\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.11","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.9","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.11","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:11","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Aussi Dieu leur envoie une puissance d\u2019\u00e9garement, pour qu\u2019ils croient au mensonge,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.12","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.10","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.12","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:12","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>afin que tous ceux qui n\u2019ont pas cru \u00e0 la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, mais qui ont pris plaisir \u00e0 l\u2019injustice, soient condamn\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.13","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.11","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.13","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:13","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-17: cf. 1 Pi 1:2-9; 5:10, 11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Pour nous, fr\u00e8res bien-aim\u00e9s du Seigneur, nous devons \u00e0 votre sujet rendre continuellement gr\u00e2ces \u00e0 Dieu, parce que Dieu vous a choisis d\u00e8s le commencement pour le salut, par la sanctification de l\u2019Esprit et par la foi en la v\u00e9rit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.14","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.12","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.14","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:14","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>C\u2019est \u00e0 quoi il vous a appel\u00e9s par notre \u00c9vangile, pour que vous poss\u00e9diez la gloire de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.15","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.13","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.15","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:15","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ainsi donc, fr\u00e8res, demeurez fermes, et retenez les instructions que vous avez re\u00e7ues, soit par notre parole, soit par notre lettre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.16","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.14","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.16","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:16","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.002.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Que notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ lui-m\u00eame, et Dieu notre P\u00e8re, qui nous a aim\u00e9s, et qui nous a donn\u00e9 par sa gr\u00e2ce une consolation \u00e9ternelle et une bonne esp\u00e9rance,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.17","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.15","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.17","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:17","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.2.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>consolent vos c\u0153urs, et vous affermissent en toute bonne \u0153uvre et en toute bonne parole!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.16","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc589b919.78649641');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc589b919.78649641\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc589b919.78649641","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc589b919.78649641'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc589b919.78649641\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}